GN5002 Discovering Creativity offered in the coming semester

Body:
GN5002 Discovering Creativity will be offered in the coming semester
(JanMay 2017)

This course will help each of one to discover several facets of creativity
 both in the outside world and within ourselves.  We will learn that
creativity is more than just idea generation.  Doing this course will help
you gain confidence in your own creativity, which in turn, will increase
the confidence in yourself.

